On today’s throwback show, Emily addresses three of the most common masturbation questions she gets asked, plus a rundown on masturbation basics.

She explains ways to masturbate in order to take your self-love to the next level, why it’s important to incorporate it into our daily lives, and where to find the elusive G-spot.
